### Policy Assistant API Endpoints
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/v1

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### ============================================
### Authentication (get token first)
### ============================================

### Login to get JWT token
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Store the token
@authToken = Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.accessToken}}

### Variables (update after creating resources)
@conversationId =
@clientId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@carrierId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

### ============================================
### Conversations
### ============================================

### Create a Guided conversation
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "mode": "Guided",
  "lineOfBusiness": "PersonalAuto"
}

### Create a Freeform conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "mode": "Freeform"
}

### List conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get a single conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### Messages (core RAG pipeline)
### ============================================

### Send a message (Guided - start)
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "content": "I need to create a personal auto insurance policy."
}

### Send a message with policy details (Freeform)
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "content": "I need a personal auto policy for John Smith with a 2022 Honda Civic. Bodily injury $100k/$300k, property damage $100k, comprehensive and collision with $500 deductible. Annual premium around $1,200. Effective January 1, 2026 for 12 months. Direct bill, annual payment."
}

### Send a message - provide carrier info
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "content": "The carrier is State Farm and the client is Sarah Johnson."
}

### ============================================
### Create Policy from Conversation
### ============================================

### Create policy from conversation extracted data
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}/create-policy
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "carrierId": "{{carrierId}}"
}

### ============================================
### Abandon Conversation
### ============================================

### Abandon a conversation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### Reference Documents (Admin)
### ============================================

### List reference documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/reference-documents
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### List reference documents filtered by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/reference-documents?category=Regulation
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Import a reference document
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy-assistant/reference-documents
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "title": "California Personal Auto Minimum Requirements",
  "category": "Regulation",
  "lineOfBusiness": "PersonalAuto",
  "state": "CA",
  "content": "California requires minimum liability coverage of $15,000 per person / $30,000 per accident for bodily injury, and $5,000 for property damage (15/30/5). Uninsured motorist coverage must be offered. Medical payments coverage is optional. The policy effective period must be at least 6 months.",
  "source": "California DMV / CDI Regulations"
}
